00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:37,980
♫ Meet someone ♫

62
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,940
♫ The world of two ♫

63
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:41,572
Fortunately.

64
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,936
Professor Zhuang!

65
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:47,876
What are you doing?

66
